rComments: An interesting professor with clear guidelines and fair marking.

I took SMC301 (Media Franchises) with him and loved the course! There were 4 written assignments worth 20% and you could write on any franchise you choose, so they were fun to write. No exam or tests, no textbook. Participation and attendance matter. The material taught was genuinely interesting and he explained everything clearly.
An awesome professor that gives great feedback. Lectures are fun and engaging, genuinely cares about his students.
Prof. Parker was awesome, very caring and funny. Loves discussion and is very insightful.
No test-taking in the course, and you are given a lot of freedom on your written work.
